connect20/folio3_maintenancemode.name: connect20/folio3_maintenanceMode

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/folio3_maintenancemode.description: The basic functionality is to put the website into Maintenance mode. Additionally this extension has a count down and it also supports IP White listing.
